OL,3,CLeeds captain signs new contract
OL,5,FThe captain of Leeds United has signed
OL,6,Fa four-year deal to keep him at the
OL,7,Fclub until 2030.
OL,9,FEthan Ampadu, 25, has established
OL,10,Fhimself as a key figure of Leeds'
OL,11,Fresurgence since his arrival from
OL,12,FChelsea FC in 2023.
OL,14,FThe midfielder was the first signing
OL,15,Fof the club's new ownership regime and
OL,16,Fbecame club captain just a year after
OL,17,Fhis first appearance.
OL,19,FAmpadu was also named Leeds' Player of
OL,20,Fthe Year in his debut season.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
