OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1780665075
OL,3,CLeeds captain signs new contract
OL,5,FHis influence at the club has remained
OL,6,Fconsistent since then, with over 100
OL,7,Fgames to his name. After the 2025-26
OL,8,Fcampaign, he collected the Player of
OL,9,Fthe Year award once more.
OL,11,FIn a statement, the club said:
OL,12,F"Everyone at Leeds United is thrilled
OL,13,FEthan has signed a new long-term deal
OL,14,Fand we look forward to seeing him
OL,15,Fcontinuing to excel at Elland Road in
OL,16,Fthe years to come".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
